productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Zoa has one of these. She works as a scribe and she says it looks wide.
The box this comes in is 4 yard by 5 inch and weights 12 pound!
It only works when I'm South Korea.
This real-time works considerably well. It mildly improves my basketball by a lot.
I saw one of these in Grenada and I bought one.
